</ul>
<p> Most of the advertising networks  provide a way to opt out of targeted and online behavioural  advertising. If you'd like to have more information about how to opt  out of the same, pay visit to&nbsp;<a href="http://www.youronlinechoices.eu/">Your  Online Choices</a>&nbsp;website.  </p>
<p id="link5"> <strong>5. What are the Online Behavioural  Advertising Cookies?</strong></p>
